Samizdat module for ruby
	
this module is usable outside of samizdat engine and provides following
classes:

 * antispam: simple wiki spam filter
 * cache: thread-safe time-limited fifo cache
 * sanitize: html validation (requires tidy)
 * storage: relational rdf storage (requires dbd::pg)


this package is a dependency package, which depends on the package
containing actual ruby samizdat module for the default ruby version
(currently 1.8).